    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300110705_36_635-665",
      "chapterUid": 36,
      "range": "635-665",
      "markText": "广成子谓黄帝曰：至阴肃肃，至阳赫赫。赫赫发乎地，肃肃出乎天。",
      "totalCount": 126,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300110705&chapterUid=36&rangeStart=635&rangeEnd=665",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f4932e40813ab91beg0155d4?chapterUid=36&rangeStart=635&rangeEnd=665"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300110705_36_1061-1080",
      "chapterUid": 36,
      "range": "1061-1080",
      "markText": "道也者，果何谓也？一言以定之，曰炁也。",
      "totalCount": 96,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300110705&chapterUid=36&rangeStart=1061&rangeEnd=1080",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f4932e40813ab91beg0155d4?chapterUid=36&rangeStart=1061&rangeEnd=1080"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300110705_36_2970-3002",
      "chapterUid": 36,
      "range": "2970-3002",
      "markText": "儒曰：存心养性。道曰：修心炼性。释曰：明心见性。心性者，本体也。",
      "totalCount": 77,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300110705&chapterUid=36&rangeStart=2970&rangeEnd=3002",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f4932e40813ab91beg0155d4?chapterUid=36&rangeStart=2970&rangeEnd=3002"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300110705_4_1344-1384",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1344-1384",
      "markText": "命有身累，则有生死。性受心役，则有去来。有生死，不能至命也。有去来，不能尽性也。",
      "totalCount": 75,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300110705&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1344&rangeEnd=1384",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f4932e40813ab91beg0155d4?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1344&rangeEnd=1384"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300110705_36_780-787",
      "chapterUid": 36,
      "range": "780-787",
      "markText": "君子终日干干。",
      "totalCount": 60,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300110705&chapterUid=36&rangeStart=780&rangeEnd=787",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f4932e40813ab91beg0155d4?chapterUid=36&rangeStart=780&rangeEnd=787"
    },
